Comment: Abilities: AEsh (Shadow Strike), Ubertip (Tooltip - Normal - Extended)
Value: Hurls a poisoned dagger at a target enemy unit, dealing <AEsh,DataE2> initial damage, and <AEsh,DataA2> damage every <AEsh,Cast2> seconds for <AEsh,Dur2> seconds. The poison slows the movement speed of the targeted unit by 75% for it's duration.
